OL,5,G2000 Casualty 24/7: Every Second Counts
OL,6,     FTwo critically ill children are
OL,7,     Frushed in by ambulance within ten
OL,8,     Fminutes of each other.
OL,9,     FTen-year-old Kai has been having
OL,10,     Fseizures, and 18-month-old Joel is
OL,11,     Fstruggling to breathe.
OL,12,G2100 999: Emergency Call Out
OL,13,     FA devastating car crash leads to a
OL,14,     Fmanhunt for the driver and two
OL,15,     Fpassengers. A man suffers brain
OL,16,     Fdamage after falling from a wall.
OL,17,     FA young cyclist endures a
OL,18,     Ftraumatic femur fracture.
